{"tid":291552,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇貝理亞可以單拖去光之國踢館？","createTime":"2017-06-20T15:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T04:59:14.000Z","uid":63913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d31249b4380e3c7ea121ae54206839a2114e127c","tid":291552,"uid":63913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T15:56:18.000Z","msg":"而一幕真係好經典。首先，佢係第一次咁具體展現出光之國（雖然太郎果時都有出過光之國，但始終只係出過短時間）。另外，貝理亞一條友可以打低幾十個超人，包括超人之父同超人兄弟；仲打到班超人好似地球人咁走難。加上其拍攝手法亦十分好，有一流特技同剪接，而唔係一般的射死光同打MMA。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nACRoKsLFFc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnACRoKsLFFc&d=ngIAoq40IwEgpsLjcmw1ajQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=90a54fb7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nACRoKsLFFc</a>"},{"pid":"59f7e82ad59d31725bab6f1a8d9d64a2704eb9e8","tid":291552,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T16:00:23.000Z","msg":"黑暗界果邊比太大力量佢？"},{"pid":"768f8cdcd933c3c1fa347dbb98544c95dccd67b2","tid":291552,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T16:03:56.000Z","msg":"太朗着火救住啲光真係好撚型"},{"pid":"64a9bd401ae5a6c8061939a022e189a81f4b7b4b","tid":291552,"uid":1803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T16:49:28.000Z","msg":"邊到有下集睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d65c232a66df6b83b15da2a455186166790424","tid":291552,"uid":33410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T18:51:40.000Z","msg":"zero後尾係咪愈黎愈多裝備<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f097dfdbebab9da2e3c0935d1da9adfcf77afd4","tid":291552,"uid":63913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T23:26:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黑暗界果邊比太大力量佢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一個人屌打全個光之國，得超人之父叫做頂到幾下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a96aa40f4807ba5030e624d4a5d1aa5